@startuml
title Insight.status lifecycle
[*] --> Proposed : new/weak evidence

Proposed --> Active : confidence >= 0.60
Active --> Contested : negative burst / strong counter-signal
Contested --> Active : reinforced by recent positives
Active --> Dormant : confidence < 0.45 (decay)
Dormant --> Retired : confidence < 0.15 (further decay or forget)
Retired --> Proposed : new evidence beyond threshold

note right of Active
Applied unless vetoed by user
or context mismatch
end note
@enduml
